	<p>This whole 'looks its the xmas season' its gonna be quiet thing is rediculous. If anything more people are on during winter than at any other time during the year. Attendance doesnt improve by february, if you havent got the players on now, when its cold, damp and miserable outside you certainly arent going to have them on when the weather improves and then heading into summer when most would rather be sat in their back gardens than in their back rooms.<br />
<br />
This decline has been happening for months. Its not scare mongering, its not jumping the gun and its not irrational or running around like a headless chicken. It is pure and simple fact.<br />
