	<!-- message -->
	<p>This waiting a few months to try to fix problems thing that some of you are pushing is the same tactic that a lot of people are pissed at SOE for using to begin with.<br />
<br />
This isn't a holiday lull that is happening.  People have moved on, and not enough are filling in behind.  Virtually my whole guild QUIT EQ.  They aren't taking a break, or going on vacation to grandma's house.  They LEFT EQ.  /cancel  Thats about 40 people.  And I highly doubt its an isolated event.<br />
<br />
Will they go back to EQ?  Maybe, maybe not.  In the meantime, the people who are still playing EQ will get more and more frusterated.<br />
<br />
Yes, wait 2-4 months.  SOE is good at not doing anything for months, so this shouldn't be a problem for them.  But its not what will help the health of EQ.</p>
	
	
	
