	<p>Just say no to premature server mergers.<br />
<br />
WoW and EQ2 probably won't kill EQ1 for a simple reason: EQ1 is chat-centric, it puts the talking and communicating part of the game front and center as the main course. The other two games, the new ones, are mostly about graphics, which are great, and arefun, but it is building relationships with online friends that really made eq1 last so long and I don't see the new games as being as condusive to that as the first eq is and was.</p>
	
	
	
